<br>
-Replace one of our DD chants with a insta cast Damage over Time (DoT).  20 second duration, 20 second recast timer.  DoTs generally do more damage over their course than direct damage spells, so this will help PvE, and allow us to use hit and run tactics in RvR.<br>
