<br>
-Increase the effectiveness of the Damage Add, make it in line with the rune master damage add (11.3 dps?).  If balancing issues arise, have it drain power while in effect.<br>
<br>
-Add in a pulsing PBAE AF-debuff chant (like the reaver).  This will help the group do more damage against the enemy, which I believe is the whole point behind the Skald.<br>
